Class JDBPrinterLineMembership

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBPrinterLineMembership
public class JDBPrinterLineMembership extends Object
The JDBPrinterLineMembership class associates physical printers with a production line and updates the table SYS_PRINTER_LINE_MEMBERSHIP
